text: CKVL may represent: * CKVL-FM 100.1, a radio station in LaSalle, Quebec, Canada * CINF 690 AM, a defunct radio station in Montreal, Quebec, Canada that used to broadcast on 850 AM as "CKVL" * CKOI-FM 96.9, a radio station in Montreal, Quebec, Canada that used to broadcast as "CKVL-FM"
title: CKVL
